text:
Not far from Adventure Playwoods and Rolling Hills, is Tembusu Lawn.
It's an open field where visitors can enjoy the expansive open space.
Sunlounger seats are strategically located by the Lawn.
New park in Bidadari full of young families and pooches. One can find a children's playground here too.

Watch birds while sleeping! There is a tree where birds often visit.

Several types of birds, including kingfishers, come and go.

Recommended for people who want to have fun watching birds! Binoculars required
